    dc:description "Figs. 7–10. Pediomorphus species, dorsal habitus. 7) P. crenulatus, holotype; 8) P. minor, holotype; 9) P. semilaevis, paratype; 10) P. punctatus, paratype. Scale bars = 1 mm." ;
